{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/gold-for-cash/","result":{"data":{"prismicProject":{"uid":"gold-for-cash","id":"9a9d0b79-b6d7-54a0-8b41-8a88cddcd3c6","data":{"project_title":{"html":"<p>Gold for Cash</p>","text":"Gold for Cash"},"client":{"html":"<p>Oliver De Vitre</p>","text":"Oliver De Vitre"},"location":{"html":"<p>Los Angeles, US</p>","text":"Los Angeles, US"},"team":{"html":"<p>Theo Ford</p>","text":"Theo Ford"},"year":{"html":"<p>2023</p>","text":"2023"},"categories":[{"category":{"slug":"logo","id":"ZMfW2BAAACMAPszy"}},{"category":{"slug":"identity","id":"ZMfWyhAAACEAPsyd"}},{"category":{"slug":"website","id":"ZMfW6RAAACMAPs1H"}},{"category":{"slug":"development","id":"ZMfW-BAAACMAPs2b"}}],"body1":[{"id":"text$33e77eb7-cd5c-48fe-94a8-1d9b4ce8e220","slice_type":"text","primary":{"text":{"html":"<p>Identity and website design &amp; build for Los Angeles based advertising consultancy Gold for Cash – founded by Oliver De Vitre (previous Nike, R/A). Oliver was interested in references from 90’s postmodernity. My approach was to honour key elements of those designers, but create something that didn’t feel like a pastiche, would fit in in today&#39;s landscape and age well. </p><p>The ambition on the site was to have a long scroll of content, so the user wouldn’t have to navigate to different pages so I came up with a simple layout system that created rhythm and variation, interspersing pull quotes advertising his approach within the projects. Once the underlying grid was in place, a level of boldness was created through an animated background that revealed parts of the grid, and use of the neon yellow drawing reference of the visual landscape of pawn shops.</p>","text":"Identity and website design & build for Los Angeles based advertising consultancy Gold for Cash – founded by Oliver De Vitre (previous Nike, R/A). Oliver was interested in references from 90’s postmodernity. My approach was to honour key elements of those designers, but create something that didn’t feel like a pastiche, would fit in in today's landscape and age well.  The ambition on the site was to have a long scroll of content, so the user wouldn’t have to navigate to different pages so I came up with a simple layout system that created rhythm and variation, interspersing pull quotes advertising his approach within the projects. Once the underlying grid was in place, a level of boldness was created through an animated background that revealed parts of the grid, and use of the neon yellow drawing reference of the visual landscape of pawn shops."}}},{"id":"video$b8eca184-ef0b-477b-9f6d-5c426678999c","slice_type":"video","primary":{"index_image":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[{"srcSet":"https://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=375&h=375&fm=webp 375w,\nhttps://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=750&h=750&fm=webp 750w,\nhttps://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=1500&h=1500&fm=webp 1500w","sizes":"(min-width: 1500px) 1500px, 100vw","type":"image/webp"}],"fallback":{"src":"https://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=1500&h=1500","srcSet":"https://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=375&h=375 375w,\nhttps://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=750&h=750 750w,\nhttps://images.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOxbVsGrYSv0ej_G4CWeb7-39-FF.jpg?auto=&fit=max&w=1500&h=1500 1500w","sizes":"(min-width: 1500px) 1500px, 100vw"}},"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#9c906e","width":1500,"height":1500}},"sml_video":{"url":"https://theoford-1.cdn.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOubVsGrYSv0ei_G4CWeb7-39-WAudio.mp4"},"video":{"url":"https://theoford-1.cdn.prismic.io/theoford-1/ZvKOubVsGrYSv0ei_G4CWeb7-39-WAudio.mp4"}}},{"id":"video$b062c78e-3f8b-4f7c-a5ad-383c7cf6c046","slice_typ